{"word":"G1284 - διαῤῥήσσω - diarrhḗssō - dee-ar-hrayce'-so - Break","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαῤῥήσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diarrhḗssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ar-hrayce'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Break</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கிழி,முறி"},{"paragraph":"to break asunder, to burst through, to rend asunder, to rend"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G4486 - ῥήγνυμι - rhḗgnymi - hrayg'-noo-mee/4486\">G4486</a>; to <i>tear asunder:</i> - break, rend.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}